forward to receiving a substantive reply to this communication. He takes note of the 
concerns brought to his attention that the execution of Mr. Ajmal Kasab in India was the 
first to have been carried out since 2004 in this country, which is after eight years of respect 
of a de facto moratorium on the implementation of the death penalty.  </p>

