<p><b>  General observations: 
</b></p>
<p>112. The Special Rapporteur regrets that the Government of Yemen has not responded to 
the communications sent during the reporting period. Given the seriousness of the 
allegations on the executions of juveniles, he urges the Government to provide substantive 
replies to both communications. The Special Rapporteur expresses concern about the 
number of cases reported to him with regard to the execution or risk of execution of </p>

<p><b>A/HRC/23/47/Add.5 
</b></p>
<p><b>64</b>  
