<p>individuals who may have been minors at the time of the offence, which would be in 
violation of international law. He calls upon the authorities in Yemen to stay all executions 
that may be carried out in contravention of international human rights law, ensure a 
thorough review of all cases, and consider commuting the death sentences. 
